    • displayScrollComponent

      void displayScrollComponent​(java.util.function.Supplier<javax.swing.JComponent> compSupplier, java.lang.String title)
      Puts a component onto a shared display of scrolling components. In other words, you should use this method to put a component onto the one scrolling component for a room. Similar to displayComponent(), previously displayed components should NOT be overwritten or otherwise made inaccessible by the displaying of a new component.
      Parameters:
      compSupplier - supplier for a scroll pane
      title - String identifier for this component. This could be a tab title for example.
